It's late in the evening
She's wondering what clothes to wear
She puts on her make up
And brushes her long blonde hair
And then she asks me
Do i look alright
And i say yes, you look wonderful tonight

We go a party
And everyone turns to see
This beautiful lady
That's walking around with me
And then she asks me
Do you feel alright
And i say yes, i feel wonderful tonight

I feel wonderful
Because i see the love light in your eyes
And the wonder of it all
Is that you just don't realize
How much i love you

It's time to go home now
And i've got an aching head
So i give her the car keys
She helps me to bed
And then i tell her
As i turn out the light
I say my darling, you were wonderful tonight
Oh my darling, you were wonderful tonight

This song makes me think of my kayla so much every time that i hear it. I just wanted her to know that i love her so much and that there is nothing that i wouldnt do for her. I think that i may have finally found the one girl that i have always been looking for.

You are Toilet Paper.



You are used and taken advantage of by a lot of people, including your friends. They make you be the one to clean up their messes in their life. But the only reason that this happens is because of your kindness and commitment. These are the qualities most members of the opposite sex look for, which makes you hot. Yes, toilet paper is hot. But be careful that your lover doesn't use you to their advantage, and be sure that they are not seeking too much control. Remember: Toilet paper is used by many, but is most often considered valuable when it is not there in time of need.

Most compatible with: sock.

wow my very first entry, so this is new to me but how can i get caught again, ya know. i thought i covered my tracks pretty well but i guess i didnt, wow invade my privacy a little more. for those of you that are wondering heres what happened: me and josh go to this party on new years eve right so ya know i drink a little nothing serious didnt get completely smashed if ya know what i mean, but the thing is for me to go anywhere i had to give my grandparents the phone # of the house i was staying at but i didnt want to give them the number of this house cause there wouldnt be anyone sober to answer the phone, so i call up my buddy cody and ask him to cover for me and i would owe him one so he was like ok man. but i came home the next day i wasnt hung over or anything and i had a  good day with  my family ya know shootin some guns with my grandpa and what not but i also talked to some friends on yahoo(brittany and caitlin...dont worry guys it was my dumbass fault for leaving it on duh) but anyway so this is the part i hate they went through my message archive and found my chats with the girls and called codys mom, who they are good freinds with, and ask her to aske him a bunch of questions about that night. and of course she got it out of him, cause for those of you that dont know codys mom she is a little intimidating, and so he leaked but i dont blame him they already knew anyway so what did it matter. so now im stuck on my ass till my b-day(feb 23) with no car and no cell phone and hardly anything else to do.
